What is selector? 

h1{
    color:blue;
}

Types of selector?
1. Tag Selector
2. group of tag Selector 
3. class selector 
4. ID Selector 
5. group of class or / and id selector 
6. universal Selector 

CSS Selector duty is , styles reusebility

Note: Nearest styles has highest prority .

